description:
VegaSviri - is the professional astrology iPhone program combines accurate calculation, visibility, smart description and a wide range of special techniques. The graphic forecast - is the pulse of your life. 

  It can:
- build single one-wheel chart (natal,transit, solar);

- start chart from Aries(left/right) or from Asc (left/right);

- build double wheel chart (natal/transit, natal/progression, natal/directions, natal/solar);

- swipe up to show ephemerides and aspects between planets and movable points (such as the moon's
nodes) under each chart;

- allow time shifts of any chart (in zoom mode as well);

- zoom chart by two fingers or double-tap;

- save, load, change natal data in DB;

- enter the birthplace of both the base cities in the world, and directly from the map;

- allow manual editing local time in difference of GMT for a specific location;

- build a weekly graphic forecast based on transit aspects to radix;

- swipe forward / backward to rebuild weekly graphic forecast in the future or in the past;

- lists the aspects by the tap on the   graphic forecast at the moment;

- build a single day graphic forecast by double tap on a weekly graphic;

- displays the author's text description of the horoscope; 

- change settings of interface and functionality of the program;

Author: Pavel Sviridov
Created by: Egor Mitrofanov
